content: Amazing tool but partially cit ofg please reconfigure resolution
It has some good ideas, but some of the ideas dont make scence.

I'm constantly searching for writing prompt generators and first line generators- anything to get me writing. This app runs fine, but lacks some features that other apps in the category have. For instance- if I like a generated answer, I can't just copy it to my clipboarr or send it to myself. Also, the quality of the content needs some work. All the ones that popped up for me were odd and poorly structured.
The IOS version has a save option for ur favorite prompts and stuff... Wish this one had that.
